96%F0%9D%91%9B%20%F0%9D%91%9C%F0%9D%91%9B%20%F0%9D%91%A1%E2%84%8E%F0%9D%91%92%20%F0%9D%91%A4%F0%9D%91%96%F0%9D%91%9B%F0%9D%91%91%20%F0%9D%91%8E%F0%9D%91%9B%F0%9D%91%91%20%F0%9D%91%9F%F0%9D%91%8E%F0%9D%91%96%F0%9D%91%9B%EF%BC%8E\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 70, 138)\">𝐴𝑖𝑛’ 𝑡 𝑛𝑜 𝑙𝑜𝑣𝑒 𝑖𝑛 𝑂𝑘𝑙𝑎ℎ𝑜𝑚𝑎<br>𝐽𝑢𝑠𝑡 𝑡ℎ𝑒 𝑤ℎ𝑖𝑠𝑡𝑙𝑒 𝑜𝑓 𝑎 𝑙𝑜𝑛𝑔 𝑏𝑙𝑎𝑐𝑘 𝑡𝑟𝑎𝑖𝑛<br>𝑌𝑜𝑢’ 𝑙𝑙 𝑘𝑛𝑜𝑤 𝑤ℎ𝑒𝑛 𝑖𝑡’𝑠 𝑐𝑜𝑚𝑖𝑛’ 𝑓𝑜𝑟 𝑦𝑎<br>𝑅𝑖𝑑𝑖𝑛’ 𝑖𝑛 𝑜𝑛 𝑡ℎ𝑒 𝑤𝑖𝑛𝑑 𝑎𝑛𝑑 𝑟𝑎𝑖𝑛．</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">𝗔𝗶𝗻’𝘁 𝗡𝗼 𝗟𝗼𝘃𝗲 𝗜𝗻 𝗢𝗸𝗹𝗮𝗵𝗼𝗺𝗮 𝗯𝘆 𝗟𝘂𝗸𝗲 𝗖𝗼𝗺𝗯𝘀</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 70, 138)\">♡︎</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 70, 138)\">𝐂𝐨𝐧𝐜𝐞𝐩𝐭:</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Brooks has always been a wild child and constantly will be. He does rodeos for a living and enjoys doing it as well as riding horses. His father passed away from cancer when he was 17, causing his brothers and him to pick up the slack and run the farm. It’s now in the hands of three brothers Dalton, Brooks, and James.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 70, 138)\">♡︎</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">I watched Twisters and Glen Powell is all I can think of now along with this Luke Combs song. The Southern in me is clawing its way out. Also, ALMOST TO 2000!! YAYAYA!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Thank you to the wonderful, <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/efb2afab-885c-4bf8-85e9-3ca2b336b2ad_profile-of-honeymilktea-555Honeymilk555Honeymilktea555\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 70, 138)\">Honeymilktea555</span> </a>for the image of Brooks and helping my broke self. I couldn’t have managed to have this picture for my bot without her!!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 70, 138)\">♡︎</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝐂𝐨𝐦𝐦𝐢𝐬𝐨𝐧𝐬 𝐚𝐫𝐞 <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSduHLn_dWaVohX-miSEr3zarMn4M9lj656MpMYXKshLoEByoQ/viewform?usp=pp_url%F0%9D%90%A1%F0%9D%90%9E%F0%9D%90%AB%F0%9D%90%9E!\" rel=\"noope","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"c94c5c49-1170-41f2-a296-642420e91cf5_c489b754-6382-4787-ba80-00824a96c820.webp","creator":"letsh3xmen","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","👤 AnyPOV","💽 Music Mania"],"chats":1361,"messages":30343,"created_at":"2024-08-05T06:06:50.730632+00:00"}